{
  "stem": "11882.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, with the Brazilian embassy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He talked these things over at our family table.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He had long talks.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And gradually, I learned a lot of German from being here and listening to their talks and asking questions and being told quite a little.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this German group, German consular group in Berlin, thought that it would be very nice if he would set up a tablecloth factory, and the Silesian weavers and textile makers were-- were really very famous.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And if he would bring his know how to Brazilian, to Brazil, and perhaps be able to bring from Hitler-- I say Hitler, I mean from Germany, of course-- a certain amount of capital, they too, the Brazilians, would invest in that because it looked like a flourishing possibility.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He had tremendous know how.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was one of the most prospering textile plants in all Germany.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He told me proudly once when he came back from Berlin, 'I just got a credit for $500,000.' Marks, I should say, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he didn't need the credit.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He didn't have a factory.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But it showed that he was a man of-- you know, he was a financial man.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that was part of his accomplishment in life, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And-- but this didn't materialize, and it was very late in the day.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was-- When I left there, it was spring '39.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And of course, we know the war started in September.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But stupid Jane Lester didn't know that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I tell you, I had a good American education, and they taught me that Wilson had said World War I was the war to end all wars.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And anything that Hitler did or the armies marching, that was just-- that didn't mean anything because no fool would start another war.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
